doc.previous: As maps can be politically charged it is important to cite your sources and or your methodology when editing or creating any map This is particularly true for historical maps
doc.after: Map styles is a subject of on going discussion at Wikipedia talk WikiProject Maps Please join in the conversation there For general use the following is a gallery of maps that have been approved by Wikiproject Maps as exemplars
